ch.lambdaj.collection
Class LambdaCollections

java.lang.Object
  ch.lambdaj.collection.LambdaCollections

public final class LambdaCollections
extends Object

This class consists exclusively of static methods that allow to create LambdaCollections.

Author:
Gianfranco Tognana, Mario Fusco
